          "Authors": "The Hinode XRT Consortium: Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics (USA); Japan Aerospace Exploration Agency (Japan); National Astronomical Observatory of Japan (Japan); NASA Marshall Space Flight Center (USA); NASA Goddard Space Flight Center (USA)",
